    "body": "They should be in the temp directory.\r\n\r\nSomething like:\r\n\r\n```js\r\npath.join(app.getPath('temp'), app.getName() + ' Crashes')\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe `productName` specified to the crash reporter will be used instead of `app.getName()` if present.\r\n\r\nYou can see the code at https://github.com/electron/electron/blob/e708a45496b9a9621e6c1f16aa039f700a2aba14/lib/common/api/crash-reporter.js#L81-L84"
